                        <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="def1-398-18580405 t18580405-398-punishment-40"></join>Confined Nine Months</rs>.</hi>
               </p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="largeCaps">HEARN</hi>—<hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <rs id="t18580405-398-verdict-2" type="verdictDescription">
